data.name: golfInstructionsLabel.Text
data.value:
1. Select a golf course from the dropdown
2. Preview the actions that will run
3. In TTR, go to the golf course and stand at the tee
4. Click 'Start Golf' and switch to TTR quickly
5. The bot will auto-swing!
Tip: Create custom actions for courses not listed.

data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value: Note: Before starting to train, call your doodle and have it's profile box open; meaning the box that shows the feed, scratch & call option etc. Also, the bot will say the trick two times, incase the doodle gets confused the first time.
